   <refnamediv>
       <refname>tsmat_names</refname>
               <refpurpose>Changes how the names of a tsmat are modified after an operation </refpurpose>
   </refnamediv>
 
        <refsynopsisdiv>
               <title>CALLING SEQUENCE</title>
               <synopsis>tsm=tsmat_names(opt)</synopsis>
        </refsynopsisdiv>
 
        <refsection>
           <title>PARAMETERS</title>
           <variablelist>
           <varlistentry>
 
           <term>Input</term>
 
<listitem><para>*  <term> argi </term> =    nothing, 'trace' or 'var'</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>&#160;&#160;-&#160;if&#160;nothing:&#160;load&#160;the&#160;default&#160;mode&#160;i.e.&#160;variable&#160;names&#160;remain&#160;the&#160;same&#160;after&#160;each&#160;operation</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>&#160;&#160;-&#160;if&#160;'trace':&#160;operations&#160;made&#160;on&#160;the&#160;data&#160;are&#160;contained&#160;in&#160;the&#160;names;&#160;ex:&#160;a&#160;log&#160;transform&#160;on&#160;a&#160;tsmat&#160;with&#160;names&#160;x&#160;and&#160;y,&#160;will&#160;create&#160;a&#160;tsmat&#160;with&#160;names&#160;log(x)&#160;and&#160;log(y)</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>&#160;&#160;-&#160;if&#160;'reset':&#160;tsmat&#160;names&#160;are&#160;changed&#160;into&#160;'var1',...,'varn'&#160;after&#160;each&#160;operation</para></listitem>
 
 
 
 
 
<listitem><para>&#160;</para></listitem>
 
           </varlistentry>
 
          <varlistentry>
 
          <term>Output</term>
 
<listitem><para>* nothing, the corresponding functions are loaded </para></listitem>
 
 
          </varlistentry>
          </variablelist>
        </refsection>
 
        <refsection>
               <title>DESCRIPTION</title>
Changes how the names of a tsmat are modified after an operation.
 
 
        </refsection>
 
        <refsection>
               <title>EXAMPLE</title>
              <programlisting role="example"><![CDATA[
 tsmat_names('trace');// the 'trace' mode is selected: the type of each operation performed on a tsmat is specified in its name.
 
               ]]></programlisting>
        </refsection>
 
        <refsection>
               <title>AUTHOR</title>
